# Group 工作重點

## 工作重點 [/api/dailyReport]

### 取得每日工作重點 [POST /api/dailyReport{?day}]

+ parameters
    + day : 20230301 (number , required) - 西元年+兩位數月+兩位數日期

+ response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "sales":"David",
            "day-point":[
                            "義大利優惠方案Flyer",
                            "錄製OG操作教學",
                            "OSOM測試"
                        ],
            "report":[
                        "義大利優惠方案Flyer (完成)",
                        "錄製OG操作教學 (待續)",
                        "OSOM測試 (待續)"
                    ]
        }

### 新增工作 [POST /newReport]

+ request (application/json)

        {
            "sales":"David",
            "day-point":[
                            "義大利優惠方案Flyer",
                            "錄製OG操作教學",
                            "OSOM測試"
                        ],
            "report":[
                        "義大利優惠方案Flyer (完成)",
                        "錄製OG操作教學 (待續)",
                        "OSOM測試 (待續)"
                    ]
        }

+ response 200 (application/json)

        新增成功

### 修改工作 [POST /editReport{?day,sales}]

+ parameters
    + day : 20230301 (number , required) - 西元年+兩位數月+兩位數日期
    + sales : David (string , required) - 業務姓名

+ request (application/json)

        {
            "sales":"David",
            "day-point":[
                            "義大利優惠方案Flyer",
                            "錄製OG操作教學",
                            "OSOM測試"
                        ],
            "report":[
                        "義大利優惠方案Flyer (完成)",
                        "錄製OG操作教學 (待續)",
                        "OSOM測試 (待續)"
                    ]
        }

+ response 200 (application/json)

        修改成功
        
### 刪除工作 [POST /deleteReport{?day,sales}]

+ parameters
    + day : 20230301 (number , required) - 西元年+兩位數月+兩位數日期
    + sales : David (string , required) - 業務姓名
    
+ response 200 (application/json)

