+ parameters
    + ID: '202352' (number, required) - 西元年+第幾週(兩位數)
    
+ request (application/json)

        {
            "ID":202301,
            "fileName":"檔名",
            "filePath":"",
            "uploadTime":"2023.03.06 21:00"
